    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2010-04-15</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2010-05-17T16:59:07Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Surreptitious Video Surveillance Act of 2010 - Amends the federal criminal code to prohibit the unauthorized video surveillance of an individual who: (1) is in an area of a temporary or permanent residence that is not readily observable from a public location; and (2) has a reasonable expectation of privacy in the area. Prohibits (with exceptions) the use of such surveillance as evidence.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Surreptitious Video Surveillance Act of 2010</title>
